---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
---

<PageLayout title="Cookie Policy" description="How Unleft uses cookies.">
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 px-4">
      <Badge className="mb-6 bg-accent-primary/10 text-accent-glow border-none mx-auto w-fit">Legal & Safety</Badge>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8 tracking-tighter" style={{ fontFamily: "'Bruno Ace SC', sans-serif" }}>
        Cookie <span class="text-accent-primary">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Managing your digital footprint. How we use cookies to enhance your experience.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-mono text-accent-glow uppercase tracking-widest">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-accent-primary/5 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-[#2D2D44] bg-[#0A0A0F]/60 p-8 md:p-12 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:text-text-primary prose-p:text-text-secondary prose-li:text-text-secondary prose-a:text-accent-glow max-w-none prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:mb-6">
          <h2>1. What Are Cookies</h2>
          <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help us provide a better browsing experience.</p>
      
          <h2>2. Cookies We Use</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto my-8 border border-[#2D2D44] rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
              <thead class="bg-[#1A1A2E]/50">
                <tr>
                  <th class="p-4 border-b border-[#2D2D44]">Type</th>
                  <th class="p-4 border-b border-[#2D2D44]">Purpose</th>
                  <th class="p-4 border-b border-[#2D2D44]">Duration</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-b border-[#2D2D44]/50">
                  <td class="p-4">Essential</td>
                  <td class="p-4">Cookie consent preference</td>
                  <td class="p-4">1 year</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="p-4">Analytics</td>
                  <td class="p-4">Traffic analysis (Vercel Analytics)</td>
                  <td class="p-4">Session</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
      
          <h2>3. Managing Cookies</h2>
          <p>You can manage your cookie preferences through the cookie banner on first visit. You can also clear cookies through your browser settings at any time.</p>
      
          <h2>4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p>We may use Google reCAPTCHA for spam protection, which sets its own cookies. These are governed by <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      
          <h2>5. Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about our cookie practices, contact <a href="mailto:hello@Unleft.space">hello@Unleft.space</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
